## Success Metric

The model must meet **all** thresholds to pass the `model_eval` gate:

| Metric | Threshold | Rationale |
|--------|-----------|-----------|
| [e.g., Precision] | ≥ [e.g., 0.85] | [e.g., "False positives waste analyst time"] |
| [e.g., Recall] | ≥ [e.g., 0.70] | [e.g., "Missing 30% of anomalies is acceptable for v1"] |
| [e.g., Inference latency] | ≤ [e.g., 50ms p95] | [e.g., "API SLA requires sub-100ms response"] |

